<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DNASPEC - 架构设计规范</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db 0%, #8e44ad 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #34495e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 5rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #f1c40f);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        nav {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            padding: 1.2rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links li {
            margin: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        main {
            min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
        }

        .section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
        }

        .section:nth-child(even) {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
        }

        .section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

        .section h2:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 140px;
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #3498db, #9b59b6);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .architecture-principles {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }

        .principle-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-left: 6px solid #8e44ad;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .principle-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .principle-card:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #8e44ad, #3498db);
        }

        .principle-card h3 {
            color: #8e44ad;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.7rem;
        }

        .principle-card p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .principle-card ul {
            margin-left: 1.8rem;
        }

        .principle-card li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .system-architecture {
            background: white;
        }

        .architecture-diagram {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin: 4rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .qualitative-side {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }

        .quantitative-side {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe 0%, #00f2fe 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.3);
        }

        .integration-center {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43e97b 0%, #38f9d7 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(67, 233, 123, 0.3);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .integration-center h4 {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .integration-center p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .skill-architecture {
            background: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .skills-structure {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.8rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .skill-structure-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.8rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-top: 5px solid #f39c12;
        }

        .skill-structure-card h3 {
            color: #d35400;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .skill-structure-card h4 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
        }

        .skill-structure-card p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .skill-structure-card ul {
            margin-left: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .lifecycle-integration {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #e4edf5 100%);
        }

        .lifecycle-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(380px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .lifecycle-integration-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-left: 6px solid #27ae60;
            position: relative;
        }

        .lifecycle-integration-card:before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #27ae60, #f1c40f);
        }

        .lifecycle-integration-card h3 {
            color: #27ae60;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

        .lifecycle-integration-card p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .lifecycle-integration-card ul {
            margin-left: 2rem;
        }

        .lifecycle-integration-card li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .agentic-integration {
            background: white;
        }

        .agentic-components {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .agentic-component-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            border-left: 5px solid #9b59b6;
        }

        .agentic-component-card h3 {
            color: #8e44ad;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .agentic-component-card p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .implementation-guidelines {
            background: #f5f7fa;
        }

        .guidelines-list {
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }

        .guideline-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
            border-left: 5px solid #3498db;
        }

        .guideline-item h3 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .guideline-item p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .guideline-item ul {
            margin-left: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .guideline-item li {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .phase-label {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0 0.5rem 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .example-box {
            background: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }

        .example-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .example-code {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 0.8rem 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #34495e 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
        }

        .footer-content p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .section h2 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .architecture-diagram {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                grid-template-rows: auto auto auto;
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .nav-links li {
                margin: 0.3rem 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>DNASPEC 架构设计规范</h1>
            <p>综合集成研讨厅架构：定性定量融合系统设计原则与实现规范</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#intro">架构概述</a></li>
            <li><a href="#principles">核心原则</a></li>
            <li><a href="#system-arch">系统架构</a></li>
            <li><a href="#skills-arch">技能架构</a></li>
            <li><a href="#lifecycle">生命周期集成</a></li>
            <li><a href="#agentic">Agentic集成</a></li>
            <li><a href="#guidelines">实现指南</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <!-- 架构概述 -->
        <section id="intro" class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>综合集成研讨厅架构概述</h2>
                <p class="intro">未来每个系统都是综合集成研讨厅，融合定性定量两种处理方式。定性部分以思维链和提示词优化为主，以置信度审核和多源多维度思考的共识计算为判断准则；定量部分则通过明确的、可固化的逻辑和算法，以代码方式实现。两个部分通过智能接口层协同工作，形成统一连贯的智能体体验。</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 核心原则 -->
        <section id="principles" class="section principles-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>核心设计原则</h2>
                <p class="intro">系统架构遵循认知过程的格式塔原则，确保系统各部分形成统一连贯的整体</p>

                <div class="architecture-principles">
                    <div class="principle-card">
                        <h3>格式塔认知完整性</h3>
                        <p>系统各部分应形成统一、连贯的整体，遵循:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>接近性原则：相关的功能在界面和功能逻辑上靠近</li>
                            <li>相似性原则：相似的功能采用统一的交互方式</li>
                            <li>连续性原则：功能流程保持一致的逻辑连续性</li>
                            <li>闭合性原则：系统提供完整的功能闭环体验</li>
                            <li>整体性原则：各部分协同工作形成统一智能体验</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="principle-card">
                        <h3>自顶向下分解原则</h3>
                        <p>从整体概念出发，逐步分解为具体的、可执行的功能模块，确保分解过程中的逻辑一致性:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>保持目标一致性：各级任务目标对齐</li>
                            <li>确保逻辑连贯性：维护任务间的逻辑关系</li>
                            <li>防止任务冲突：避免职责不清和重复劳动</li>
                            <li>维持上下文完整性：保持任务上下文的内聚性</li>
                            <li>遵循格式塔认知：确保分解后的部分形成整体</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="principle-card">
                        <h3>局部智能体架构原则</h3>
                        <p>通过局部智能体处理复杂用户意图，避免全局上下文膨胀，实现智能体社会架构:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>上下文隔离：每个智能体专注局部上下文，防止全局污染</li>
                            <li>专业分工：智能体按领域和专业能力分工</li>
                            <li>模块化设计：智能体本身具备模块化特性</li>
                            <li>可扩展性：支持智能体数量和能力的有序增长</li>
                            <li>协调协议：智能体间具备标准化协作协议</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="principle-card">
                        <h3>定性定量融合原则</h3>
                        <p>将确定性逻辑用代码固化，不确定性部分用智能体处理，需要用户决策的模糊问题以最直观的方式呈现:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>确定性固化：将可固化的逻辑用代码实现</li>
                            <li>不确定性智能处理：将不确定分析交由智能体</li>
                            <li>用户决策界面：将模糊问题以决策问答形式呈现</li>
                            <li>接口层协调：统一协调定性定量处理</li>
                            <li>智能决策融合：结合定性定量信息做决策</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="principle-card">
                        <h3>宪法需求管理原则</h3>
                        <p>基于初始宪法需求实现动态约束、版本管理、时间点恢复机制，确保系统演进不偏离初心:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>需求锁定：将初始需求设为宪法版本</li>
                            <li>变更追踪：持续追踪需求变更历史</li>
                            <li>对齐检查：验证新需求与宪法的一致性</li>
                            <li>时间恢复：支持时间点快照和回滚</li>
                            <li>需求演进：允许必要时的宪法修订流程</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="principle-card">
                        <h3>渐进式增长原则</h3>
                        <p>系统从简单到复杂平稳增长，每步增长建立在坚实基础上，遵循KISS、YAGNI、SOLID原则:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>步进式发展：每次只添加必要的复杂度</li>
                            <li>坚实基础：每步都建立在前步的稳定基础上</li>
                            <li>KISS原则：保持每部分简单清晰</li>
                            <li>YAGNI原则：只实现当前需要的功能</li>
                            <li>SOLID原则：确保代码结构遵循设计原则</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 系统架构 -->
        <section id="system-arch" class="section system-architecture">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>定性定量综合集成架构</h2>
                <p class="intro">系统采用三层架构模式，确保定性定量处理的深度融合与有效协同</p>

                <div class="architecture-diagram">
                    <div class="qualitative-side">
                        <h4>定性引擎</h4>
                        <p>思维链推理 (Chain of Thought)</p>
                        <p>提示词优化 (Prompt Optimization)</p>
                        <p>置信度审核 (Confidence Assessment)</p>
                        <p>共识计算 (Consensus Calculation)</p>
                        <p>用户意图理解 (User Intent Understanding)</p>
                        <p>创造性分析 (Creative Analysis)</p>
                        <p>多维度推理 (Multi-Dimensional Reasoning)</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="integration-center">
                        <h4>智能接口层</h4>
                        <p>定性定量协同 (Qualitative/Quantitative Coordination)</p>
                        <p>智能决策融合 (Intelligent Decision Fusion)</p>
                        <p>任务分配与路由 (Task Allocation & Routing)</p>
                        <p>上下文管理 (Context Management)</p>
                        <p>用户意图解析 (User Intent Parsing)</p>
                        <p>结果反馈机制 (Result Feedback)</p>
                        <p>不确定性评估 (Uncertainty Assessment)</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="quantitative-side">
                        <h4>定量引擎</h4>
                        <p>算法模块 (Algorithm Modules)</p>
                        <p>数据处理 (Data Processing)</p>
                        <p>逻辑验证 (Logic Verification)</p>
                        <p>性能计算 (Performance Calculation)</p>
                        <p>确定性逻辑 (Deterministic Logic)</p>
                        <p>代码执行 (Code Execution)</p>
                        <p>标准化接口 (Standardized Interfaces)</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="intro">
                    <p><strong>定性引擎：</strong>处理模糊、不确定或复杂问题，应用认知框架和思维链，以置信度审核和共识计算为判断准则。</p>
                    <p><strong>定量引擎：</strong>处理确定性、可固化的计算任务，具有明确的输入输出关系，通过代码精确实现。</p>
                    <p><strong>智能接口层：</strong>协调定性定量处理，融合智能决策，管理用户交互，确保统一连贯的智能体体验。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 技能架构 -->
        <section id="skills-arch" class="section skill-architecture">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>技能架构设计</h2>
                <p class="intro">围绕综合集成研讨厅理念设计的技能系统，每个技能都支持定性定量融合，实现全生命周期发展</p>

                <div class="skills-structure">
                    <div class="skill-structure-card">
                        <h3>上下文工程技能族</h3>
                        <p>上下文分析、优化和认知模板技能，支持AI开发中的上下文管理，防止上下文爆炸和腐化。</p>
                        
                        <h4>功能职责:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>上下文质量评估 - 五维度分析（清晰度、相关性、完整性、一致性、效率）</li>
                            <li>上下文优化 - AI驱动改进上下文质量</li>
                            <li>认知框架应用 - 链式思维、少样本学习、验证、角色扮演</li>
                            <li>格式塔认知完整性 - 保持整体概念一致性</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p class="example-title">使用示例:</p>
                        <div class="example-code">/dnaspec.context-analysis "用户认证系统架构设计" --detail-level enhanced</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="skill-structure-card">
                        <h3>系统设计技能族</h3>
                        <p>架构师、模块化等技能，支持系统从简单到复杂的设计演进，防止架构失控。</p>
                        
                        <h4>功能职责:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>架构设计 - 支持微服务、单体等多种架构风格</li>
                            <li>模块分解 - 将系统分解为可重用模块</li>
                            <li>接口定义 - 定义清晰的模块接口</li>
                            <li>依赖管理 - 管理模块间依赖关系</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <p class="example-title">使用示例:</p>
                        <div class="example-code">/dnaspec.architect "电商平台架构" --style microservices</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="skill-structure-card">
                        <h3>Agentic技能族</h3>
                        <p>任务分解、约束生成、智能体创建等技能，实现局部智能体架构，防止上下文膨胀。</p>
                        
                        <h4>功能职责:</h4>
                        <ul>
